'''大士彎地鐵站'''（{{lang-en|Tuas Crescent MRT Station}}，代號'''EW31'''）是[[新加坡地鐵東西線|新加坡地鐵東西線]]上的车站，位于[[新加坡|新加坡]]本岛[[大士_(新加坡)|大士]]规划区。该站因靠近一条同名街道而得名。

==歷史==
2011年1月11日，新加坡交通部長[[林雙吉|林雙吉]]曾在造訪[[勿洛地鐵站|勿洛地鐵站]]新式[[全高式月台門|全高式月台門]]系統時透露，將建設新的東西線延伸段，即大士南支線。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.lta.gov.sg/data/apps/news/press/2011/20110111%20Tuas%20West%20-%20Speech.pdf |title=SPEECH BY MR RAYMOND LIM, MINISTER FOR TRANSPORT AND - 20110111 Tuas West - Speech.pdf |publisher=[[陸路交通管理局|land transport authority]] |date=2011-01-11 |accessdate=2016-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161127214657/https://www.lta.gov.sg/data/apps/news/press/2011/20110111%20Tuas%20West%20-%20Speech.pdf |archive-date=2016-11-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.mot.gov.sg/News-Centre/Highlights/Circle-Line-and-Tuas-West-Extension-updates/ |title=Circle Line and Tuas West Extension updates |publisher=Ministry Of Transport |date=2011-01-11 |accessdate=2016-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161127155419/https://www.mot.gov.sg/News-Centre/Highlights/Circle-Line-and-Tuas-West-Extension-updates/ |archive-date=2016-11-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>新路線預定在2016年完工，每天將使約100,000名乘客受益。<ref>{{cite web | url=https://surbanajurong.com/sector/tuas-west-mass-rapid-transit-mrt-extension-depot/ | title=Tuas West Mass Rapid Transit (MRT) Extension Depot | publisher=Surbana Jurong | date= | accessdate=August 29, 2016 | archive-date=2018-01-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180126132056/https://surbanajurong.com/sector/tuas-west-mass-rapid-transit-mrt-extension-depot/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2016年10月26日時，為了一同與東西南北線新設置的信號系統，官方宣布大士彎地鐵站會延後至2017年6月18日開放。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.lta.gov.sg/apps/news/page.aspx?c=2&id=9293b7de-5142-47a7-ad16-9148ecd41db2 |title=The Rail Report: New Signalling System, Rail Line and Extension and Trains Next Year |publisher=[[陸路交通管理局|land transport authority]] |date=2016-10-26 |accessdate=2016-11-05 |archive-date=2016-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161026170955/https://www.lta.gov.sg/apps/news/page.aspx?c=2&id=9293b7de-5142-47a7-ad16-9148ecd41db2 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.zaobao.com.sg/znews/singapore/story20161027-682580 |title=南北线新信号系统需更多测试 大士西延长线延至明年第二季通车 |publisher=[[聯合早報|聯合早報]] |date=2016-10-27 |accessdate=2016-11-25 |archive-date=2016-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161101020541/http://www.zaobao.com.sg/znews/singapore/story20161027-682580 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

